                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> to <span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span></p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The crew strikes with belaying pins, hooks, and cutlasses at enemies in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5] (@Check[reflex|dc:19|basic] save). The damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[1d6[bludgeoning]]{1d6 bludgeoning, piercing, or slashing damage}</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(2d6+4)[bludgeoning]]{2d6+4 bludgeoning, piercing, or slashing damage}</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(3d6+6)[bludgeoning]]{3d6+6 bludgeoning, piercing, or slashing damage}</p>"
                },
